description: Partial details pursuant to conditions 3 and 27 of permission granted on 21st January 2005 (reg. no. 2002/2037) for development of the former Power Station for leisure and entertainment use and redevelopment of the surrounding land for commercial and residential purposes.  The details relate to the Power Station, the West Hotel/railway station, the office/product showcase buildings, the residential building and the theatre, and ancillary/associated spaces, and include:-Siting, design, external appearance;  treatments of associated parts of the site not covered by buildings; access and facilities for people with disabilities; taxi parking and servicing provision; refuse storage/disposal arrangements, and sewers; and, the designation of green and brown roofs on the West Hotel/railway station, the office/product showcase building, the residential building and Power Station, and provision for nesting including provision on the Power Station for peregrine falcons.
